Package: lancedbr
Type: Package
Title: LanceDB Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Cathal", "Byrne",
      email = "cathal470@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides an R interface to LanceDB, a vector database
    built on Apache Arrow. The package offers a backend-agnostic API
    for creating tables, adding data, and performing vector similarity
    search. The initial implementation uses the Python LanceDB client
    via the 'reticulate' package, with a design intended to support a
    future native Rust backend.
